flowchart LR
  Operator[Software Factory operator] --> Browser[Browser authenticated shell]
  Browser --> Route[/tasks/create route]
  Route --> Page[TaskCreationPage]
  Page --> Form[TaskCreationForm]
  Form --> Tokens[TaskCreationForm generated tokens]
  Design[DESIGN.md] --> Generator[scripts/generate-design-tokens.mjs]
  Generator --> Tokens
  Generator --> GlobalTokens[src/app/design-tokens.css]
  GlobalTokens --> PageStyles[src/app/styles.css task-create page styles]
  Tokens --> Form
  PageStyles --> Page
  Form --> Payload[title + raw_requirements payload]
  Payload --> Api[Existing POST /tasks API]
  Api --> Draft[Intake Draft response]
  Draft --> Success[Dark success state with title first]
